nodes.title: Generation steps
widgets_values:
1. Generate 00 full body front view. (bypass if you already got one)
2. Generate 01-03 side and back views.
3. Generate as needed: 04-07 (medium) | 08-11 (close-up) | 12-15 (extreme close-up)
4. Generate 16-19 head close-up.
5. Generate 24-31 facial action and expression. change types as needed.
6. Generate as needed: 20-23(focus). change view type to item you want to focus.
7. Generate 32-35 (random). change random sheet resolution, refs, prompts as needed.
Keep the subject features exactly the same.
